        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">The PV pf bamboo pole was calculated on the PV of bamboo culm. Similar to the Ecuadorian dataset, it was assumed that 30 % of the harvested bamboo culms are used for construction materials. The PV was adjusted based on the differences in dry mass of bamboo culm and bamboo pole. </productionVolumeComment>
